NORTH AMERICAN OIL CONSOLIDATED, Petitioner, v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE, Respondent. No. 6599. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 29, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

*1082PER CÜRIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for respondent, consented to by counsel for petitioner, ordered petition to review of North American Oil Consolidated dismissed; mandate forthwith.
